trans-unit.source: Provides a set of methods and properties that enable applications to trace the execution of code and associate trace messages with their source.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder et sett med metoder og egenskaper som gjør at programmer kan spore kjøring av kode, og knytt sporingsmeldinger til kilden.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceSource"></xref> class, using the specified name for the source.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceSource"> </xref> class, ved hjelp av det angitte navnet for datakilden.

trans-unit.source: The source name is used to identify traces.
trans-unit.target: Kildenavnet brukes til å identifisere sporinger.

trans-unit.source: It is used by a <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceFilter> to determine whether a trace listener should produce the trace.
trans-unit.target: Den brukes av en <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceFilter>å finne ut om en lytter for sporingen må produsere sporingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceFilter>

trans-unit.source: The recommended practice is to use the name of the application for the source name.
trans-unit.target: Den anbefalte fremgangsmåten er å bruke navnet på programmet for kildenavnet.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > It is not necessary to create a new <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> instance for each trace request.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Er det ikke nødvendig å opprette et nytt <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>forekomsten for hver sporing av forespørsel.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>

trans-unit.source: Create one <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> instance and use it for all trace requests for the application.
trans-unit.target: Opprett en <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>serverforekomsten og bruke den for alle sporingsforespørsler for applikasjonen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>

trans-unit.source: The name of the source (typically, the name of the application).
trans-unit.target: Navnet på datakilden (vanligvis navnet på programmet).

trans-unit.source: name is .
trans-unit.target: nameis .

trans-unit.source: name is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: nameen tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceSource"></xref> class, using the specified name for the source and the default source level at which tracing is to occur.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceSource"> </xref> klassen, ved hjelp av det angitte navnet for kilden og standard kilde-nivå på som sporing er kan utføres.

trans-unit.source: The source name is used to identify traces.
trans-unit.target: Kildenavnet brukes til å identifisere sporinger.

trans-unit.source: It can be used by a <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> to determine if tracing is to occur and by a <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceFilter> to determine whether to produce the trace.
trans-unit.target: Den kan brukes av en <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>å avgjøre om sporing er oppstår og ved en <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceFilter>om skal produsere sporingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceFilter> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>

trans-unit.source: The default source level is used by an <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventTypeFilter> to determine if tracing is to occur based on the source level of the message to be traced.
trans-unit.target: Det standard beskyttelsesnivået for datakilden er brukt av en <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventTypeFilter>å avgjøre om sporing er oppstår basert på kilde-nivået for meldingen som skal spores.</xref:System.Diagnostics.EventTypeFilter>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > It is not necessary to create a new <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> instance for each trace request.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Er det ikke nødvendig å opprette et nytt <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>forekomsten for hver sporing av forespørsel.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>

trans-unit.source: Create one <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> instance and use it for all trace requests for the application.
trans-unit.target: Opprett en <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>serverforekomsten og bruke den for alle sporingsforespørsler for applikasjonen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>

trans-unit.source: The name of the source, typically the name of the application.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på datakilden, vanligvis navnet på programmet.

trans-unit.source: A bitwise combination of the enumeration values that specifies the default source level at which to trace.
trans-unit.target: En bitvis kombinasjon av nummereringsverdier som angir hvilket standard kildenivå til sporing.

trans-unit.source: name is .
trans-unit.target: nameis .

trans-unit.source: name is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: nameen tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets the custom switch attributes defined in the application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Henter attributtene for egendefinerte switch som er definert i programmets konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: The Attributes property identifies the custom attributes referenced in the application's configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen attributter identifiserer de egendefinerte attributtene som det refereres til i programmets konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: Unreferenced custom attributes are not enumerated.
trans-unit.target: Ubrukte egendefinerte attributter listes ikke.

trans-unit.source: Classes that inherit from the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> class can add custom attributes by overriding the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.GetSupportedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method and returning a string array of custom attribute names.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som arver fra den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>klassen kan legge til egendefinerte attributter ved å overstyre den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.GetSupportedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden og returnere en strengmatrise for egendefinert attributtnavn.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.GetSupportedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>

trans-unit.source: The following is a sample of a trace source element specifying the custom attribute `SecondTraceSourceAttribute`: ``` <sources> <source name="TraceTest" switchName="TestSourceSwitch" switchType="Testing.MySourceSwitch, TraceSample" SecondTraceSourceAttribute="two"> </source> </sources> ```
trans-unit.target: Følgende er et eksempel på sporingen kildeelement angivelse av det egendefinerte attributtet `SecondTraceSourceAttribute`:``` <sources> <source name="TraceTest" switchName="TestSourceSwitch" switchType="Testing.MySourceSwitch, TraceSample" SecondTraceSourceAttribute="two"> </source> </sources> ```

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary"></xref> containing the custom attributes for the trace switch.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary"> </xref> som inneholder de egendefinerte attributtene for bryteren sporingen.

trans-unit.source: Closes all the trace listeners in the trace listener collection.
trans-unit.target: Lukker alle sporingslyttere i sporingen lytteren samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Close method calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Close%2A> method of each trace listener in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Lukk metodekall den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Close%2A>metode for hver trace-lytteren i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Close%2A>

trans-unit.source: Flushes all the trace listeners in the trace listener collection.
trans-unit.target: Tømmer alle sporingslyttere i sporingen lytteren samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Flush method calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Flush%2A> method of each trace listener in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall tømming av <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Flush%2A>metode for hver trace-lytteren i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Flush%2A>

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to trace an event during finalization.
trans-unit.target: Forsøkte å spore en hendelse under finalization.

trans-unit.source: Gets the custom attributes supported by the trace source.
trans-unit.target: Henter de egendefinerte attributtene som støttes av sporingskilden.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation for GetSupportedAttributes returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Standardimplementering for GetSupportedAttributes returnerer `null`.

trans-unit.source: A string array naming the custom attributes supported by the trace source, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if there are no custom attributes.
trans-unit.target: En strengmatrise navngi egendefinerte attributter støttes av sporingskilden, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis det er ingen egendefinerte attributter.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of trace listeners for the trace source.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av sporingslyttere for sporing av datakilden.

trans-unit.source: Use this property to access and perform operations on the trace listeners.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne egenskapen tilgang til og kan utføre operasjoner på sporingslyttere.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection"></xref> that contains the active trace listeners associated with the source.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection"> </xref> som inneholder de aktive sporingslyttere knyttet til kilden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the trace source.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på sporingskilden.

trans-unit.source: The name is set by the `name` parameter passed to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Navnet er angitt av den `name` -parameteren sendt til konstruktøren.

trans-unit.source: You can refer to the trace source by using the `name` attribute in the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Du kan referere til trace-datakilde ved hjelp av `name` attributtet i konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: The following XML element shows referring to a trace source in the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Følgende XML-elementet viser refererer til en sporingskilden i konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: The name of the trace source.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på sporingskilden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the source switch value.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir switch kildeverdien.

trans-unit.source: The Switch property allows the filtering of messages before the trace source calls the listeners.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Switch tillater filtrering av meldinger før spore kilde samtaler i lyttere.

trans-unit.source: The switch is used to check whether trace calls should be generated or ignored.
trans-unit.target: Bryteren brukes til å kontrollere om spore samtaler skal genereres eller ignorert.

trans-unit.source: Each trace method calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> method of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> to determine whether to proceed with the trace.
trans-unit.target: Hver trace-metoden kaller den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>å finne ut om du vil sporingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the call returns `true`, the listeners are called.
trans-unit.target: Hvis kallet returnerer `true`, lyttere kalles.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch"></xref> object representing the source switch value.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch"> </xref> -objekt som representerer switch kildeverdien.

trans-unit.source: Switch is set to <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Switch er satt til <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Writes trace data to the trace listeners in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*> collection using the specified event type, event identifier, and trace data.
trans-unit.target: Skriver sporingsdata trace-lyttere i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>samlingen ved hjelp av den angitte hendelsestype hendelses-ID og sporingsdata.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>

trans-unit.source: The TraceData method, like the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%2A> method, is intended for automated tools, but it also allows the attaching of an additional object, such as an exception instance, to the trace.
trans-unit.target: Metoden TraceData, like den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%2A>metoden, er ment for automatiserte verktøy, men gjør det også mulig å knytte til et ekstra objekt, for eksempel en unntak-forekomst for sporingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%2A>

trans-unit.source: The TraceData method calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> object returned by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall TraceData den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>objektet som ble returnert av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> returns `true`, TraceData calls the corresponding <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceData%2A> method on all listeners.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>returnerer `true`, TraceData kaller den tilsvarende <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceData%2A>-metoden på alle lyttere.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceData%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, TraceData returns without calling the listeners' methods.
trans-unit.target: Ellers returneres TraceData uten å kalle metoder, lyttere.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener> object is limited to a maximum `id` value of 65,535.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>objektet er begrenset til maksimum `id` verdien 65 535.</xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: If the `id` value specified is greater than 65,535, the <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener> object uses 65,535.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `id` angitte verdien er større enn 65 535, den <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>objekt bruker 65 535.</xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: One of the enumeration values that specifies the event type of the trace data.
trans-unit.target: En av opplistingsverdiene som som angir hendelsestypen for av sporingsdataene.

trans-unit.source: A numeric identifier for the event.
trans-unit.target: En numerisk identifikator for hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The trace data.
trans-unit.target: Sporingsdata.

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to trace an event during finalization.
trans-unit.target: Forsøkte å spore en hendelse under finalization.

trans-unit.source: Writes trace data to the trace listeners in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*> collection using the specified event type, event identifier, and trace data array.
trans-unit.target: Skriver sporingsdata trace-lyttere i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>samlingen ved hjelp av den angitte hendelsestype hendelses-ID og sporingen data matrise.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>

trans-unit.source: The TraceData method, like the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%2A> method, is intended for automated tools, but it also allows the attaching of additional objects, such as an exception instance and a stack trace, to the trace.
trans-unit.target: Metoden TraceData, like den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%2A>metoden, er ment for automatiserte verktøy, men gjør det også mulig å knytte flere objekter, for eksempel en unntak-forekomst og en stakksporing til sporing.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%2A>

trans-unit.source: The TraceData method calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> method of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> object returned by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall TraceData den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>objektet som ble returnert av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> returns `true`, TraceData calls the corresponding <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceData%2A> method on all listeners.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>returnerer `true`, TraceData kaller den tilsvarende <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceData%2A>-metoden på alle lyttere.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceData%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, TraceData returns without calling the listeners' methods.
trans-unit.target: Ellers returneres TraceData uten å kalle metoder, lyttere.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener> object is limited to a maximum `id` value of 65,535.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>objektet er begrenset til maksimum `id` verdien 65 535.</xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: If the `id` value specified is greater than 65,535, the <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener> object uses 65,535.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `id` angitte verdien er større enn 65 535, den <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>objekt bruker 65 535.</xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: One of the enumeration values that specifies the event type of the trace data.
trans-unit.target: En av opplistingsverdiene som som angir hendelsestypen for av sporingsdataene.

trans-unit.source: A numeric identifier for the event.
trans-unit.target: En numerisk identifikator for hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: An object array containing the trace data.
trans-unit.target: Et objektmatrise som inneholder sporingsdata.

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to trace an event during finalization.
trans-unit.target: Forsøkte å spore en hendelse under finalization.

trans-unit.source: Writes a trace event message to the trace listeners in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*> collection using the specified event type and event identifier.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en sporingen hendelsesmeldingen til sporingslyttere i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>samlingen ved hjelp av den angitte hendelsestype og hendelses-IDen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>

trans-unit.source: The TraceEvent method is intended to trace events that can be processed automatically by tools.
trans-unit.target: Metoden TraceEvent skal sporingshendelser som kan behandles automatisk av verktøy.

trans-unit.source: For example, a monitoring tool can notify an administrator if a specific event is traced by a specific source.
trans-unit.target: Et overvåking verktøy kan for eksempel varsle en administrator om en bestemt hendelse spores av en bestemt datakilde.

trans-unit.source: The TraceEvent method calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> method of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> object returned by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall TraceEvent den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>objektet som ble returnert av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> returns `true`, TraceEvent calls the corresponding <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A> method of each listener.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>returnerer `true`, TraceEvent kaller den tilsvarende <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A>metode for hver lytteren.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, TraceEvent returns without calling the listeners' methods.
trans-unit.target: Ellers returneres TraceEvent uten å kalle metoder, lyttere.

trans-unit.source: The trace content is listener specific.
trans-unit.target: Sporingsinnholdet er lytteren bestemte.

trans-unit.source: If the method is not overridden by the listener implementation, the default output is the name of the trace source, its numeric identity, and the event type.
trans-unit.target: Hvis metoden ikke overstyres av lytteren implementeringen, er standard utdata navnet på sporingskilden, numerisk identiteten og hendelsestypen.

trans-unit.source: Additional trace content is dependent upon the listener's <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceOutputOptions%2A> property value.
trans-unit.target: Ekstra sporingsinnholdet er avhengig av lytteren for <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceOutputOptions%2A>egenskapsverdi.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceOutputOptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener> object is limited to a maximum `id` value of 65,535.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>objektet er begrenset til maksimum `id` verdien 65 535.</xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: If the `id` value specified is greater than 65,535, the <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener> uses 65,535.

trans-unit.source: The TraceInformation method provides an informational message intended to be read by users and not by tools.
trans-unit.target: Metoden TraceInformation gir en Informasjonsmelding som skal leses av brukere og ikke av verktøy.

trans-unit.source: TraceInformation calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%28System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.String%29> method, setting `eventType` to <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=fullName> and passing the informative message as the message string.
trans-unit.target: TraceInformation kall den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%28System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.String%29>metoden innstillingen `eventType` til <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=fullName>og sende informativ melding som meldingen-streng.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.TraceEvent%28System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.String%29>

trans-unit.source: Writes a trace transfer message to the trace listeners in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*> collection using the specified numeric identifier, message, and related activity identifier.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en sporingen overføring melding til sporingslyttere i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>samlingen ved hjelp av den angitte numerisk identifikator melding og relaterte aktivitets-ID.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>

trans-unit.source: The TraceTransfer method calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceTransfer%2A> method of each trace listener in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A> property to write the trace information.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall TraceTransfer den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceTransfer%2A>metode for hver trace-lytteren i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A>til å skrive informasjon om spørringssporingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceTransfer%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceTransfer%2A> method in the base <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> class calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%28System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Diagnostics.TraceEventType%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.String%29?displayProperty=fullName> method to process the call, setting `eventType` to <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=fullName> and appending a string representation of the `relatedActivityId` GUID to `message`.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceTransfer%2A>metoden i grunntallet <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>klasse kall av <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%28System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Diagnostics.TraceEventType%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.String%29?displayProperty=fullName>metode for å behandle samtalen, innstillingen `eventType` til <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=fullName>og legge til en strengrepresentasjon av den `relatedActivityId` GUID til `message`.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%28System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Diagnostics.TraceEventType%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.String%29?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceTransfer%2A>

trans-unit.source: TraceTransfer is intended to be used with the logical operations of a <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>.
trans-unit.target: TraceTransfer skal brukes med logiske operatorer for <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>

trans-unit.source: The `relatedActivityId` parameter relates to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A> property of a <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager> object.
trans-unit.target: Den `relatedActivityId` parameteren som er knyttet til den <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A>for en <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>objektet.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager> </xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A>

trans-unit.source: If a logical operation begins in one activity and transfers to another, the second activity logs the transfer by calling the TraceTransfer method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en logisk operasjon starter i én aktivitet og overfører til en annen, logger den andre aktiviteten overføringen ved å kalle metoden TraceTransfer.

trans-unit.source: The TraceTransfer call relates the new activity identity to the previous identity.
trans-unit.target: Kallet TraceTransfer ny aktivitets-ID i forhold til tidligere identiteten.

trans-unit.source: The most likely consumer of this functionality is a trace viewer that can report logical operations that span multiple activities.
trans-unit.target: Mest sannsynlige forbruker for denne funksjonen er en sporingen viewer som kan rapportere logiske operasjoner som går over flere aktiviteter.
